rows.label: bf11490100_0010
rows.name:
Oh, you mean that time?
I remember. What about it?

rows.label: bf11490100_0030
rows.name:
I think he was talking about Metsu, but his
words could just as easily have applied to Marveni.

rows.label: bf11490100_0050
rows.name: What if all of this is what Marveni-

rows.label: bf11490100_0060
rows.name: No, what all of humanity really wants?

rows.label: bf11490100_0085
rows.name:
What are we going to do if we
defeat Metsu anyway?

rows.label: bf11490100_0100
rows.name: Like I told Hugo, go home and work the land.

rows.label: bf11490100_0105
rows.name: I didn't get to harvest the Gromrice this year.

rows.label: bf11490100_0110
rows.name: While that might be good enough for you...

rows.label: bf11490100_0130
rows.name: Some others might...not be too pleased with that...
